<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 400 400">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="skyGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#87CEEB" />
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#C6E6FB" />
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  
  <!-- Background -->
  <rect width="400" height="400" fill="url(#skyGradient)" />
  
  <!-- Bicycle -->
  <g id="bicycle">
    <!-- Wheels -->
    <circle cx="120" cy="300" r="40" fill="none" stroke="#333" stroke-width="4" />
    <circle cx="280" cy="300" r="40" fill="none" stroke="#333" stroke-width="4" />
    <circle cx="120" cy="300" r="35" fill="none" stroke="#555" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="5,5" />
    <circle cx="280" cy="300" r="35" fill="none" stroke="#555" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="5,5" />
    
    <!-- Frame -->
    <path d="M120,300 L200,300 L240,220 L160,220 Z" fill="none" stroke="#E74C3C" stroke-width="6" />
    <line x1="200" y1="300" x2="240" y2="220" stroke="#E74C3C" stroke-width="6" />
    <line x1="240" y1="220" x2="280" y2="300" stroke="#E74C3C" stroke-width="6" />
    <line x1="240" y1="220" x2="240" y2="180" stroke="#E74C3C" stroke-width="6" />
    
    <!-- Handlebars -->
    <path d="M240,180 C255,170 265,185 270,180" fill="none" stroke="#E74C3C" stroke-width="4" />
    
    <!-- Pedals -->
    <circle cx="200" cy="300" r="12" fill="#555" />
    <line x1="190" y1="290" x2="210" y2="310" stroke="#333" stroke-width="6" />
    <circle cx="190" cy="290" r="5" fill="#777" />
    <circle cx="210" cy="310" r="5" fill="#777" />
    
    <!-- Seat -->
    <ellipse cx="160" cy="220" rx="15" ry="5" fill="#333" />
  </g>
  
  <!-- Pelican -->
  <g id="pelican">
    <!-- Body -->
    <ellipse cx="200" cy="175" rx="45" ry="35" fill="white" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1" />
    
    <!-- Head and neck -->
    <path d="M230,160 C250,150 260,125 245,105 C240,95 225,95 220,105" 
          fill="white" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1" />
    
    <!-- Beak -->
    <path d="M220,105 L270,95 L235,120 L220,105 Z" fill="#F9A825" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1" />
    <path d="M220,105 L235,120 L220,115 Z" fill="#F57F17" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1" />
    
    <!-- Eye -->
    <circle cx="225" cy="102" r="3" fill="#333" />
    
    <!-- Wings -->
    <path d="M190,160 C160,130 150,155 160,175 C170,195 190,185 190,170" 
          fill="white" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1" />
    
    <!-- Legs -->
    <path d="M215,210 L240,240" stroke="#F9A825" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
    <path d="M240,240 L243,177" stroke="#F9A825" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
    
    <!-- Feet -->
    <path d="M243,177 L250,182" stroke="#F9A825" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
    <path d="M240,240 L245,245" stroke="#F9A825" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
    
    <!-- Tail -->
    <path d="M155,175 L140,165 L135,175 L140,185 L155,180" 
          fill="white" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1" />
  </g>
  
  <!-- Ground -->
  <rect x="0" y="340" width="400" height="60" fill="#8D6E63" />
  <rect x="0" y="340" width="400" height="10" fill="#A1887F" />
</svg>

<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 400 400">
  <!-- Bicycle -->
  <g id="bicycle">

    <circle cx="100" cy="300" r="40" fill="none" stroke="#333" stroke-width="3"/>
    <circle cx="100" cy="300" r="36" fill="none" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,2"/>
    <circle cx="100" cy="300" r="5" fill="#333"/>
    
    <circle cx="280" cy="300" r="40" fill="none" stroke="#333" stroke-width="3"/>
    <circle cx="280" cy="300" r="36" fill="none" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,2"/>
    <circle cx="280" cy="300" r="5" fill="#333"/>
    
    <!-- Frame -->
    <line x1="100" y1="300" x2="190" y2="300" stroke="#4682B4" stroke-width="6"/>
    <line x1="190" y1="300" x2="280" y2="300" stroke="#4682B4" stroke-width="6"/>
    <line x1="190" y1="300" x2="150" y2="230" stroke="#4682B4" stroke-width="6"/>
    <line x1="150" y1="230" x2="240" y2="230" stroke="#4682B4" stroke-width="6"/>
    <line x1="240" y1="230" x2="280" y2="300" stroke="#4682B4" stroke-width="6"/>
    
    <!-- Handlebar -->
    <line x1="150" y1="230" x2="120" y2="200" stroke="#4682B4" stroke-width="4"/>
    <line x1="120" y1="200" x2="140" y2="180" stroke="#333" stroke-width="3"/>
    <line x1="120" y1="200" x2="100" y2="190" stroke="#333" stroke-width="3"/>
    
    <!-- Seat -->
    <ellipse cx="240" cy="230" rx="15" ry="5" fill="#333"/>
    
    <!-- Pedals -->
    <circle cx="190" cy="300" r="15" fill="none" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2"/>
    <line x1="190" y1="285" x2="175" y2="270" stroke="#333" stroke-width="4"/>
    <rect x="170" y="265" width="10" height="5" fill="#333"/>
    <line x1="190" y1="315" x2="205" y2="330" stroke="#333" stroke-width="4"/>
    <rect x="200" y="330" width="10" height="5" fill="#333"/>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Pelican -->
  <g id="pelican">
    <!-- Body -->
    <ellipse cx="195" cy="160" rx="45" ry="30" fill="#F5F5F5" stroke="#DDD" stroke-width="1"/>
    
    <!-- Wings -->
    <path d="M195 170 C 220 180, 230 210, 240 230 C 230 220, 215 215, 195 220 Z" fill="#F5F5F5" stroke="#DDD" stroke-width="1"/>
    <path d="M195 170 C 180 180, 170 200, 165 220 C 175 215, 185 215, 195 220 Z" fill="#F5F5F5" stroke="#DDD" stroke-width="1"/>
    
    <!-- Head and Neck -->
    <path d="M185 135 C 180 125, 175 120, 160 120 C 150 120, 145 125, 145 130 C 145 140, 155 145, 170 145 Z" fill="#F5F5F5" stroke="#DDD" stroke-width="1"/>
    <path d="M195 160 C 195 150, 190 140, 185 135" fill="none" stroke="#F5F5F5" stroke-width="10"/>
    
    <!-- Beak -->
    <path d="M145 130 C 125 127, 110 133, 105 135 C 100 137, 100 140, 105 142 C 115 145, 125 140, 145 130 Z" fill="#FFA500" stroke="#FF8C00" stroke-width="1"/>
    
    <!-- Eye -->
    <circle cx="160" cy="125" r="3" fill="#000"/>
    
    <!-- Legs -->
    <path d="M195 190 C 195 200, 190 230, 190 250 L 190 285" fill="none" stroke="#FFA500" stroke-width="3"/>
    <path d="M195 190 C 200 200, 210 230, 215 250 L 225 285" fill="none" stroke="#FFA500" stroke-width="3"/>
    
    <!-- Feet -->
    <path d="M190 285 C 185 290, 180 290, 175 285" fill="none" stroke="#FFA500" stroke-width="3"/>
    <path d="M225 285 C 230 290, 235 290, 240 285" fill="none" stroke="#FFA500" stroke-width="3"/>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Background Elements -->
  <g id="background" opacity="0.3">
    <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="15" fill="#87CEEB"/>
    <circle cx="350" cy="80" r="20" fill="#87CEEB"/>
    <circle cx="320" cy="40" r="10" fill="#87CEEB"/>
  </g>
</svg>

<svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="skyGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#87CEEB"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#E6F7FF"/>
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  
  <!-- Background -->
  <rect x="0" y="0" width="400" height="400" fill="url(#skyGradient)"/>
  
  <!-- Ground -->
  <rect x="0" y="300" width="400" height="100" fill="#8BC34A"/>
  
  <!-- Bicycle -->
  <g transform="translate(200, 300) scale(0.9)">
    <!-- Bicycle Frame -->
    <path d="M-50,-30 L0,0 L40,-30 L0,-70 Z" fill="none" stroke="#D32F2F" stroke-width="6"/>
    <line x1="0" y1="0" x2="-20" y2="30" stroke="#D32F2F" stroke-width="6"/>
    
    <!-- Wheels -->
    <g id="frontWheel" transform="translate(40, -30)">
      <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="30" fill="none" stroke="#333" stroke-width="4"/>
      <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="25" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="2,3"/>
      <g>
        <line x1="-25" y1="0" x2="25" y2="0" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="0" y1="-25" x2="0" y2="25" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="-18" y1="-18" x2="18" y2="18" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="-18" y1="18" x2="18" y2="-18" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2"/>
      </g>
    </g>
    
    <g id="backWheel" transform="translate(-50, -30)">
      <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="30" fill="none" stroke="#333" stroke-width="4"/>
      <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="25" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="2,3"/>
      <g>
        <line x1="-25" y1="0" x2="25" y2="0" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="0" y1="-25" x2="0" y2="25" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="-18" y1="-18" x2="18" y2="18" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="-18" y1="18" x2="18" y2="-18" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2"/>
      </g>
    </g>
    
    <!-- Handlebars -->
    <path d="M40,-30 C50,-50 60,-40 60,-30" fill="none" stroke="#D32F2F" stroke-width="4"/>
    
    <!-- Pedals -->
    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="8" fill="#666"/>
    <line x1="0" y1="0" x2="12" y2="15" stroke="#333" stroke-width="3"/>
    <circle cx="12" cy="15" r="5" fill="#333"/>
    
    <!-- Seat -->
    <ellipse cx="0" cy="-70" rx="10" ry="5" fill="#4B2E2E"/>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Pelican -->
  <g transform="translate(190, 200)">
    <!-- Body -->
    <ellipse cx="0" cy="0" rx="30" ry="25" fill="#F5F5F5"/>
    
    <!-- Head -->
    <circle cx="20" cy="-35" r="15" fill="#F5F5F5"/>
    
    <!-- Beak -->
    <path d="M25,-40 L60,-35 L25,-30" fill="#FFA000" stroke="#E65100" stroke-width="1"/>
    <path d="M25,-40 L60,-35 L25,-30" fill="none" stroke="#E65100" stroke-width="1"/>
    <ellipse cx="58" cy="-35" rx="5" ry="2" fill="#E65100"/>
    
    <!-- Pouch -->
    <path d="M20,-30 Q30,-15 20,-5" fill="none" stroke="#FFA000" stroke-width="2"/>
    
    <!-- Eye -->
    <circle cx="25" cy="-40" r="2" fill="#000"/>
    
    <!-- Wings -->
    <path d="M-5,-5 Q-20,-30 -40,-5 Q-20,0 -5,5" fill="#EEEEEE" stroke="#BDBDBD" stroke-width="1"/>
    
    <!-- Legs -->
    <line x1="-10" y1="20" x2="-10" y2="30" stroke="#FFA000" stroke-width="3"/>
    <line x1="10" y1="20" x2="15" y2="5" stroke="#FFA000" stroke-width="3"/>
    
    <!-- Feet -->
    <path d="M-10,30 L-20,35 M-10,30 L-15,38 M-10,30 L-5,36" stroke="#FFA000" stroke-width="2"/>
  </g>
  
  <!-- Clouds -->
  <g fill="#FFFFFF" opacity="0.8">
    <ellipse cx="80" cy="60" rx="30" ry="20"/>
    <ellipse cx="50" cy="60" rx="20" ry="15"/>
    <ellipse cx="110" cy="60" rx="25" ry="18"/>
    
    <ellipse cx="320" cy="40" rx="25" ry="15"/>
    <ellipse cx="290" cy="40" rx="20" ry="12"/>
    <ellipse cx="350" cy="40" rx="22" ry="14"/>
  </g>
</svg>
